title: Gym Guide - Themeforest Fitness Sport Wordpress Theme
description:
Gym Guide is a wordpress theme specially designed for Gym and Fitness websites. This template is easy to modify and 

ready to be up and running out of the box. The PSD files included have been customized to allow fast skinning.

This template comes in 8 pre made color variations. But it will only take one minute to create your desired color 

schemes by using theme options

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/gym-guide-fitness-sport-wordpress-theme/6734928

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
